                <h1>Q&amp;A: St. John&#039;s athletic director Mike Cragg reflects on lessons learned over 3 decades at Duke</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e15249f0-7555-48b1-803f-6c3b5108c04f.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Current&#x20;St.&#x20;John&#x27;s&#x20;athletic&#x20;director&#x20;Mike&#x20;Cragg&#x20;returns&#x20;to&#x20;Cameron&#x20;in&#x20;Duke&#x27;s&#x20;matchup&#x20;against&#x20;St.&#x20;John&#x27;s.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Current St. John's athletic director Mike Cragg returns to Cameron in Duke's matchup against St. John's.</p>

